_properties.descriptionZh: 特定组织或业务人员的北美行业分类系统（NAICS）代码
_properties.rdfs:comment: The North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) code for a particular organization or business person.

_properties.descriptionZh: 组织的雇员数
_properties.rdfs:comment: The number of employees in an organization e.g. business.
_properties.rdfs:label: numberOfEmployees

_properties.descriptionZh: 组织或个人拥有的产品
_properties.rdfs:comment: Products owned by the organization or person.
_properties.rdfs:label: owns

_properties.descriptionZh: subOrganization的反向属性，即包含这个组织的更大组织
_properties.rdfs:comment: The larger organization that this organization is a subOrganization of, if any.
_properties.rdfs:label: parentOrganization

_properties.descriptionZh: 描述作品主要创作方的编辑原则的页面链接
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The publishingPrinciples property indicates (typically via URL) a document describing the editorial principles of an Organization (or individual e.g. a Person writing a blog) that relate to their activities as a publisher, e.g. ethics or diversity policies. When applied to a CreativeWork (e.g. NewsArticle) the principles are those of the party primarily responsible for the creation of the CreativeWork.

While such policies are most typically expressed in natural language, sometimes related information (e.g. indicating a funder) can be expressed using cnschema.org terminology.
_properties.rdfs:label: publishingPrinciples

_properties.descriptionZh: 针对某一个事物（人，文章，地点，产品）的评论
_properties.rdfs:comment: A review of the item.
_properties.rdfs:label: review

_properties.descriptionZh: 个人或组织公布的需求，用于寻求某种商品或服务。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to products or services sought by the organization or person (demand).
_properties.rdfs:label: seeks

_properties.descriptionZh: 通过质押，承诺或财政捐助支持事物的人或组织。 例如 医学研究的赞助者或事件的公司赞助商。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A person or organization that supports a thing through a pledge, promise, or financial contribution. e.g. a sponsor of a Medical Study or a corporate sponsor of an event.
_properties.rdfs:label: sponsor

_properties.descriptionZh: 两个组织之间的关系。其中第二个组织，例如以子公司的名字，属于第一个组织。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A relationship between two organizations where the first includes the second, e.g., as a subsidiary. See also: the more specific 'department' property.
_properties.rdfs:label: subOrganization

_properties.descriptionZh: 组织或个人的税/财务编号，例如 美国的TIN或西班牙的CIF / NIF
_properties.rdfs:comment: The Tax / Fiscal ID of the organization or person, e.g. the TIN in the US or the CIF/NIF in Spain.
_properties.rdfs:label: taxID

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType
